data.description: A fresh palette to build multi generational housing/ADU's or add on to the existing home to create your dream home, currently used as income property, which you could decide to continue. Amazing opportunity to own nearly 5 acres of flat land with barn and mature fruit trees. Mountain views surround you on this prime all usable lot!  Home is on public water, but also has a 450 ft deep well, small workshop, and RV hook up. Come bring your vision, Horses, RV's, dreams of a small vineyard or homesteading lifestyle. Close to the 67 and town amenities.
